rows.label: qst106001_0010
rows.name:
Hey, Dad! You feeling OK?
Your fluff look ruffly!

rows.label: qst106001_0020
rows.name:
Huh?
...Oh, it Tora.

rows.label: qst106001_0030
rows.name: Me not too bad. Tum-tum is quiet.

rows.label: qst106001_0040
rows.name:
Masterpon is careful with health.
Good food, much sleep, regular poo-poo.

rows.label: qst106001_0050
rows.name: Indeed! Body of Dadapon is temple!

rows.label: qst106001_0060
rows.name:
Too much info for Tora!
...So then, why make grumble-noise?

rows.label: qst106001_0070
rows.name: Ah, well... Thing is...

rows.label: qst106001_0080
rows.name: Was thinking of making new mode for Hana.

rows.label: qst106001_0090
rows.name:
Oh!
Tora and Dadapon have same idea!

rows.label: qst106001_0100
rows.name: Tora was thinking it about time Hana got even more Hana-power!

rows.label: qst106001_0110
rows.name: What? Tora think that too?

rows.label: qst106001_0120
rows.name: Truly Tora is sonnypon of Tatezo! Has Dadapon's ideas too!

rows.label: qst106001_0130
rows.name:
So... What was Dadapon's idea?
Tell Tora!

rows.label: qst106001_0140
rows.name:
Tora excited?
OK, Dadapon will let cat out from bag.

rows.label: qst106001_0150
rows.name: Behold! Hana's most super-duper mode.

rows.label: qst106001_0160
rows.name: W-what's this?!

rows.label: qst106001_0170
rows.name:
You like?
Tora like so much, run out of words, maybe?

rows.label: qst106001_0180
rows.name: This mode called 'Super Fighter Mode'!

rows.label: qst106001_0190
rows.name:
This Hana size of ten Rosas.
More battle power than Divine Beast warship.

rows.label: qst106001_0200
rows.name: What Dadapon thinking?!

rows.label: qst106001_0210
rows.name:
Dadapon just take old Hana blueprint
and enlarge!

rows.label: qst106001_0220
rows.name: Dadapon thinking just like Bahn...

rows.label: qst106001_0230
rows.name: What? Tora not like great big Hana?

rows.label: qst106001_0240
rows.name: Well, how about this?

rows.label: qst106001_0250
rows.name:
Uh? Hmmm...
Too small for Tora's eyesight...

rows.label: qst106001_0260
rows.name:
This is titchy little Hana.
Extreme compact.

rows.label: qst106001_0270
rows.name:
But what for...?!
...And you just changed size again...

rows.label: qst106001_0280
rows.name:
What good is itty-bitty little Hana?
Catch mice and rats maybe...

rows.label: qst106001_0290
rows.name:
Tora not see? This Hana piddly, but can
sneak in anywhere, and no one know!

rows.label: qst106001_0300
rows.name:
And battle capabilities same as normal Hana!
Strong like ant!

rows.label: qst106001_0310
rows.name:
Dadapon...
All this a bit fur-brained...

rows.label: qst106001_0320
rows.name: Not like little piddly Hana either...?

rows.label: qst106001_0330
rows.name: Well... Let's hear Tora's silly idea then.

rows.label: qst106001_0340
rows.name:
Really want to hear?
Really?!

rows.label: qst106001_0350
rows.name: All right, Tora suppose can share secret.

rows.label: qst106001_0360
rows.name:
Tora's big idea called...
Hana JD!

rows.label: qst106001_0370
rows.name: Cootie-Pie?

rows.label: qst106001_0380
rows.name: Right! Nearly...

rows.label: qst106001_0390
rows.name:
This Hana become great big grown-up.
Hana should move to next phase of life!

rows.label: qst106001_0400
rows.name: Tora and Hana grow up together!

rows.label: qst106001_0410
rows.name:
Uhm...
I know not meaning of 'QTÏ€', but...

rows.label: qst106001_0420
rows.name: Tora's unruly, lovable enthusiasm shine through, very bright!

rows.label: qst106001_0430
rows.name: Dadapon! Dadapon like it!

rows.label: qst106001_0440
rows.name:
Yes, Tora.
This make sense, for a change.

rows.label: qst106001_0450
rows.name:
Very well! Dadapon will get right to it!
Kiku! Ready my things!

rows.label: qst106001_0460
rows.name: Yes, Masterpon! At once.

rows.label: qst106001_0470
rows.name: Hear that, Hana?

rows.label: qst106001_0480
rows.name: Masterpon and Dadapon will work in chamber for a little bit.

rows.label: qst106001_0490
rows.name:
Don't let anyone disturb very very very important work!
Got it?

rows.label: qst106001_0500
rows.name: Yes, Masterpon!

rows.label: qst106001_0510
rows.name: Tora... What's the little ball of fur getting into this time?

rows.label: qst106001_0520
rows.name: Unclear...

rows.label: qst106001_0530
rows.name:
It sounded like they were going to try to
power up Hana-chan somehow.

rows.label: qst106001_0540
rows.name: I also caught some bollocks about "growing up" and "phase of life".

rows.label: qst106001_0550
rows.name: You'd know. You're the master of talking bollocks.

rows.label: qst106001_0560
rows.name: Huh? How dare you.

rows.label: qst106001_0570
rows.name: Ugh. You know exactly what I mean.

rows.label: qst106001_0580
rows.name: Well, I guess this means they're going to remodel Hana.

rows.label: qst106001_0590
rows.name: Guess so.

rows.label: qst106001_0600
rows.name:
Whatever it is, looks like they won't
be coming out of there for a while.

rows.label: qst106001_0610
rows.name: Nothing for it. Why don't we go and take a rest at the inn?

rows.label: qst106001_0620
rows.name:
Huh?
They're still at it?

rows.label: qst106001_0630
rows.name: Yes, Catlady.

rows.label: qst106001_0640
rows.name:
Masterpon working feverishly.
Not stop for food, sleep, or poo-poo.

rows.label: qst106001_0650
rows.name: Tora... He doesn't know what's good for him, sometimes.

rows.label: qst106001_0660
rows.name: He's going to work himself bald one of these days.

rows.label: qst106001_0670
rows.name: Urk!

rows.label: qst106001_0680
rows.name: My lady!

rows.label: qst106001_0690
rows.name:
Tadaa!
Master plan of Tora complete!

rows.label: qst106001_0700
rows.name:
'Master plan'? Sounds great.
But what on earth is it, Tora?

rows.label: qst106001_0710
rows.name: Meh-he-he-he...

rows.label: qst106001_0720
rows.name:
Behold!
Really something, huh?

rows.label: qst106001_0730
rows.name: Ooh!

rows.label: qst106001_0740
rows.name:
Behold!
Final and bestest form of Hana!

rows.label: qst106001_0750
rows.name: My lady... Are you quite all right?!

rows.label: qst106001_0760
rows.name: ...gyagh...

rows.label: qst106001_0770
rows.name:
Tora...!
Is this not...too much?!

rows.label: qst106001_0780
rows.name:
Only yesterday, Hana was littlepon...
Maybe she grow too fast!

rows.label: qst106001_0790
rows.name: Tora not care!

rows.label: qst106001_0800
rows.name: Tora feel that Hana is ready to be real grown-up.

rows.label: qst106001_0810
rows.name: Tora... Can you really build such advanced robo-woman?

rows.label: qst106001_0820
rows.name: Dadapon. Tora mean what he say.

rows.label: qst106001_0830
rows.name:
Destiny calling for Tora.
Rude not to say "hello" back.

rows.label: qst106001_0840
rows.name: Well said, my littlepon.

rows.label: qst106001_0850
rows.name: [ ML:undisp  ] AD LIB unease

rows.label: qst106001_0860
rows.name: Urgh...

rows.label: qst106001_0870
rows.name: Will...you...get...OFF me already...!!

rows.label: qst106001_0880
rows.name: Meh-mehh!
